{"tid":1939365,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"15歲女生涉藏汽油彈原料准保釋 事隔6個月被控管有非法用途工具罪","createTime":"2020-03-23T06:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T06:07:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c752d5a23e675c8add5dbd4ce165f457ea2d1000","tid":1939365,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"15歲中四女學生於去年9月30日，在天水圍天華路遭警方搜出酒精、白電油等汽油彈原料。事隔6個月，警方起訴她一項管有可作非法用途的工具罪，今日在屯門裁判法院少年庭提堂。她暫時毋須答辯，案件將押後至5月15日再訊，期間准以現金5000元擔保，不准離港，並須守宵禁令。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告在去年9月30日，在天水圍天華路管有一個載有乙醇的玻璃樽、一枝消毒藥水、白電油、錫紙、毛巾、白色粉末等工具。據知，當晚案發地點有人群聚集，附近一名的士司機覺得可疑而報警。"},{"pid":"cd7be66959cf997ee4f60f0c122b09b03ac8d377","tid":1939365,"uid":29649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T06:06:45.000Z","msg":"的士佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de5f11ff4db574e3f34d7441f65a49bb0ca41ee","tid":1939365,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T06:07:37.000Z","msg":"D.C. dog <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}